-- start template query54.tpl query 81 in stream 0
with /* TPC-DS query54.tpl 0.81 */ my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'rings'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 6
         and d_year = 1998
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
/*CURSOR_IDENTIFIER*/
middle:
) as aggregated_sales
inner join store s on aggregated_sales.ss_store_sk = s.s_store_sk
where s.S_REC_START_DATE <= CURRENT_DATE AND (s.S_REC_END_DATE IS NULL OR s.S_REC_END_DATE > CURRENT_DATE)
group by s.S_STORE_NAME, aggregated_sales.i_manufact_id

        , c_current_addr_sk

          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,

 select distinct c_customer_sk

                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk

         and i_class = 'rings'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 6
         and d_year = 1998
 )
 , my_revenue as (

        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk

 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
